column3:
New links collapse effective distance and commute friction; satellite nodes with bigger homes re-rate first. 


Kolkata East–West Metro (Howrah–Esplanade/Sector-V) completed in stages incl. under-river run; 

Uttan–Virar Sea Link & Talegaon–Chakan–Shikrapur corridor works raise accessibility of PCMC–Chakan and MMR’s far-suburbs; 

Bhopal Metro priority section targeted.
